snippet.title: Hearts of Olympus: Otome Game PV
snippet.description:
Break your curse, battle mythic foes, and fall for the gods in an epic tale of love and destiny!
Download 'Hearts of Olympus' to find out! 

Available on Google Play or Otomania for iOS. Check it out from the links below!

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.genius.medusaotome

Apple:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/otomani...
